Rico's Taco's in Sunset Park, Brooklyn NY is a fun, local Mexican taco place. The tacos are Mexican start to finish. If you are expecting Americanized tacos this may not be a place you want to go to, however if you are looking for a real taste of Mexico when it comes to Tacos - come here and see for yourself. It's a blast. They serve other Authetic items such as sandwiches, fish, rice, and other entrees and dishes. The service however is not very good, they are polite and make you feel important but the service is slow. You will wait a while for your food. Make sure you come on a day you are not in a rush. For that, everything else about this place is A++.
